author: Fextralife
description:
The Outer Worlds 2 Review - Better than the First Game?
In this Outer Worlds 2 review, I'll share my impressions after finishing the game and playing for the past week. In this video, we'll take a look at whether Outer Worlds 2 is better than the original game. Is it worth a day one purchase? How long is the game, and how much role-playing is there to be had? We will answer all of these things and more.
